welcome_message_body: Welcome to Moissac, a charming city known for its stunning Romanesque abbey and picturesque countryside. We hope you have a wonderful time exploring and experiencing all that our beautiful city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at La Garenne Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at La Garenne Airport, primarily used for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
